======================================================================
PART 6: THE α-VECTOR — TOPOLOGICAL TYPE OF Ω(T)
======================================================================

The OCF decomposes H = 1 + α₁·2 + α₂·4 + α₃·8 + ...
Each αₖ counts independent sets of size k in Ω(T).
The tuple (α₁, α₂, ...) is the TOPOLOGICAL fingerprint of Ω.

